:::The Destrocons/Falcon/Snare/Hun-Grr/Starscream:::

::Ramjet walks out::
Ramjet: We have negotiated our Alliance.  The three Predacon leaders have 
agreed.  Come veryone, Drillbit has allowed us to get a drink at their mess 
hall.
::All of my Destrons find their way to the mess hall. Dirge, Skywarp, Falcon 
and Snare sit down together, get an energin, and start talking about 
whatever.  Ramjet looks to Cygnar::
Ramjet: Id like to talk to you about the terms of the alliance, please sit 
down here.
::he went to a table::
~~~~~
::Hun-Grr started flying to the CF, hoping that his team will follow::
~~~~~
::Starscream walks out of the base, deciding he needs a good fly to clear his 
head. he opens his comm::
Starscream: Drillbit, im going for a fly, ill be back in a few.
::He flies around aimlessly, just trying to think::
OOC: You know what to do Logo.
